  "description": "Pure-MLX (mlx_lm) and exo perf-proxy sidecar telemetry plus the Apple distributed AllReduce fabric probe. TTFT/TPOT/throughput/KV are proxy-measured by llm_perf_proxy.py (mlx_lm and exo expose no native Prometheus metrics). Folded into hydra:llm:* via hydra-llm-normalization.yml; fabric panels use hydra:fabric:* (mlx-fabric.rules.yml).",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
